577
00:49:07,120 --> 00:49:08,590
Unacceptable.

578
00:49:12,990 --> 00:49:15,620
- Would you stop?
- Didn't work for you last time.

579
00:49:15,830 --> 00:49:17,090
What?

580
00:49:17,300 --> 00:49:19,260
You heard me.

