677
00:56:40,990 --> 00:56:44,010
Pekurovsky. Lorie Pekurovsky.

678
00:56:45,230 --> 00:56:47,280
Tell me how you really feel.

679
00:56:51,560 --> 00:56:52,790
Well, Kate.

680
00:56:53,200 --> 00:56:56,660
- Surprise, surprise.
- Hello, Brian.

681
00:57:01,510 --> 00:57:03,980
