744
01:02:15,610 --> 01:02:16,570
Look at me.

745
01:02:16,780 --> 01:02:18,400
Miss Moseley, Mr. Dorsey,
you're on.

746
01:02:18,610 --> 01:02:20,580
Look at my eyes, look at my eyes.
